<h2 class="nsw-h3">Pictogram</h2>
<p><strong>Characteristics</strong></p>
<p>The pictogram language is derived from visual cues within the brand:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Curved outer edges of logo</li>
  <li>Lines within the negative space of logo</li>
  <li>Sharp inner edges of logo</li>
  <li>Square details (referencing Public Sans)</li>
</ul>
