<h3>Sizing</h3>
<p>Pictograms should be designed on a pixel-based grid of 64px x 64px with a
  live area of 60px x 60px, and can be scaled down linearly to half size if
  required. Pictogram content should remain inside of the live area, which is
  the region of an image that is unlikely to be hidden from view (such as when
  sidebars appear upon scrolling).</p>
